00:45:12.636 --> 00:45:14.237
to what I've been doing recently,

00:45:14.277 --> 00:45:17.996
is how and from who do you acquire feedback

00:45:17.996 --> 00:45:19.237
for your dashboards?

00:45:19.237 --> 00:45:21.436
And also like, what kind of questions do you ask

00:45:21.436 --> 00:45:25.076
so you actually get the feedback that you want from them

00:45:25.076 --> 00:45:27.636
and not just leave it as free for all?

00:45:27.636 --> 00:45:28.477
Yeah, terrific.

00:45:28.477 --> 00:45:29.876
Carlos, you wanna take that one?

00:45:30.917 --> 00:45:35.436
Yeah, so I would say sometimes the best feedback

00:45:35.436 --> 00:45:39.957
that I've got is not directly in the presentations

00:45:39.957 --> 00:45:42.477
where I give, because when I do the presentation

00:45:42.477 --> 00:45:45.316
of the dashboard, the reaction that we're getting,

00:45:45.316 --> 00:45:47.876
oh, this is so cool, let me try it out

00:45:47.876 --> 00:45:51.037
and actually give them a time window.

00:45:51.037 --> 00:45:53.076
So give them the link to the dashboard

00:45:53.076 --> 00:45:54.237
to start playing with it,

00:45:54.237 --> 00:45:58.556
actually using it for around a week or so.

00:45:58.556 --> 00:46:01.237
I would say, if you're gonna give them some time

00:46:01.237 --> 00:46:03.556
to do some UAT on the dashboard,

00:46:03.556 --> 00:46:05.316
I've always found out a good tip

00:46:05.316 --> 00:46:07.076
is to give them a timeline.

00:46:07.076 --> 00:46:11.477
If you just say, do it whenever you can, that won't happen.

00:46:11.477 --> 00:46:13.436
So if you just give them a timeline

00:46:13.436 --> 00:46:15.076
and they actually going to do it,

00:46:16.037 --> 00:46:18.997
because when you do the presentation,

00:46:18.997 --> 00:46:22.436
the presentations, you actually don't get too much feedback,

00:46:22.436 --> 00:46:25.276
but the most valuable one has been in those

00:46:25.276 --> 00:46:27.717
setting up a standard UAT time

00:46:27.717 --> 00:46:30.957
and then implementing those.

